<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//5306/53069a6b3435b2edfbf9835bd06cbd30.com/large/191b0000f8acfdaa4a2b"></p> 
<p>Step 2：接着将半扎发绑成一个蓬松的丸子头。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//eb78/eb78c1a3e248c516eaf32fa9d1b665c2.com/large/1915000121b71952de9e"></p> 
<p>Step 3：然后在披散的头发一侧取一束头发绑一条三股辫。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//7ec9/7ec979c24a6b3765d4908f9c8740210a.com/large/18b100032ce3de0ffd4f"></p> 
<p>Step 4：将三股辫拉松散一些，松散的发辫让整个发型看起来更加慵懒自然。</p> 
<p><img src="http://192.168.2.201:8086//9591/95913218563b8d14cf1fc19fef6e67b8.com/large/19170001229caec4ad49"></p> 
